                    <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white">Blog</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white">Community</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white">API Documentation</a></li>
